Usage:

report_generation.py -d DIR -e FILE_EXT -o OUTPUT_FORMAT
                           (-f FAIL_STRING | -file FAIL_FILE)

DIR-------------Directory in which we need to search fail string recursively in all folders.
FILE_EXT--------File extension to be searched in DIR
OUTPUT_FORMAT---The desired format of report generation.
FAIL_STRING-----Failure string to be searched in all file with FILE_EXT
FAIL_FILE-------File which contains multiple failure strings to be searched in all file with FILE_EXT

Note: Provide either FAIL_STRING or FAIL_FILE.


Prerequisites:

This requires following python packages:
argparse --   sudo apt-get install python-argparse
xlwt     --   sudo apt-get install python-xlwt
